{
  "stem": "5430.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had to finish school, and then be allowed to be assigned to a-- to a position that they would choose and be an auto mechanic-- a mechanic for the autos and tractors.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Which, at the time, I never gave any thought about it as long as we got a good education plus a stipend, which was-- I don't remember-- all I remember big-- big ruble bills.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we had a fairly-- fairly nice life there for a few weeks or month or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was communists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- communism was the big thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the thing that-- that got bad is the fact that my brother Jacob went back to Poland to bring back more people, to rescue more people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And unfortunately, he got caught by the Russians on the border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had lead us with him, you know, to the families in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they accused him of being a spy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he was trying to go back to Poland to bring back more family, family and friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- and they-- at that time, we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I've-- we've since found out that he was sentenced as a spy and sent to Archangelsk, which is up north, the gold mines of Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Archangelsk, I think is A-R-C-H-A-N-G-E-L-S-K, Archangelsk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's a very-- a terrible prison place, labor-- labor camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And unfortunately, he-- he did not survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, we heard that he was sentenced and sent there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From other people, we saw that he was picked up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they followed the-- the tribunal or whatever the court was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know anything about after that until--",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
